### **AIQ NTA Fact Sheet Summary – June 2025**  

#### **Key Financials**  
- **NTA per unit**: AUD 1.8586 (down 2.1% MoM)  
- **Adjusted NTA per unit (1)**: AUD 1.4880 (down 1.8% MoM)  
- **Total NTA**: AUD 56.413 million  
- **Units on issue**: 30,352,483  

#### **Performance & Portfolio Update**  
- NTA declined due to FX movements (AUD/USD impact: -1.5% after hedging).  
- Received **US$437k distribution** from Warana 2023 Fund.  
- **Target distribution**: 5% of NTA p.a. (semi-annual, details to be announced).  

#### **Valuation Notes**  
- **Adjusted NTA** reflects secondary-market discounts (discounted cash flows at 10% p.a.).  
- NTA includes unaudited third-party fund valuations (lagged 6-8 weeks).  

#### **Liquidity & Tax**  
- **Accumulated tax losses**: >AUD 400m (may offset future taxable income).  
- **Accumulated capital losses**: >AUD 20m.  

#### **Top Portfolio Exposures**  
- **King Street Special Investments** (15.6% of NTA)  
- **Fortress PE Funds** (13.5%)  
- **WSS Kings LP** (6.4%)  
- **Cash & equivalents**: AUD 4.4m (7.8% of NTA).  

#### **FX Exposure**  
- **USD dominance**: 59% of portfolio (partially hedged).  
- **AUD/USD rate**: 0.6582 (2.3% MoM move).  

**No material corporate actions or capital structure changes identified.**
